description:
NetconfTls table:  Records of Netconf TLS configurations for Ericsson radio access network elements.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
- Area_Name: Geographic area of the network element.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant Cell ID.
- Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely redundant).
- Id4: Ancillary identifier (likely redundant).
- vsDataType:  Data type identifier specifying Netconf TLS data.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- NetconfTls.port: Port number used for Netconf TLS communication.
- NetconfTls.administrativeState: Administrative state of the Netconf TLS connection (e.g., LOCKED, UNLOCKED).
- NetconfTls.nodeCredential:  Node credentials for Netconf TLS authentication.
- NetconfTls.trustCategory: Trust category assigned to the Netconf TLS connection.
- NetconfTls.netconfTlsId: Unique identifier for the Netconf TLS configuration.
